            <lg xml:id="TK1107">
<l>tammi liruntu tamatupāt tuṇṭaṟṟā </l>
<l>lammā varivai muyakku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The embraces of a gold-complexioned beautiful female are as pleasant as to dwell in one's own house and live by one's own (earnings) after distributing (a portion of it in charity).</l>
            </lg>
